{"tid":1103831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登有愛－麵包超人飛走左","createTime":"2019-04-12T16:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T17:45:45.000Z","uid":231051,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"62fcf4a6b2e32c8e47d36c690c969e16e18d20cc","tid":1103831,"uid":231051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:14:44.000Z","msg":"話說小弟每日死慳死抵每日唔坐車行路翻學 中午自己匿埋一邊食麵包<br />\n儲儲埋埋食夠百幾個麵包之後終於可以係photoday召喚到個麵包超人比女朋友<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRGVMBx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRGVMBx.jpg&h=54182aa4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n女朋友都好開心超人玩<br />\n但影到差唔多尾聲嘅時候，個麵包超人就飛走左<br />\n可能佢覺得已經完成任務，要繼續將歡樂帶比其他人<br />\n所以佢選擇左離開我地<br />\n我一路望住佢飛，一路諗，佢一個只係塑膠造成嘅超人，但卻係有住宏大而寬廣嘅夢想<br />\n唔理身軀嘅限制，帶住佢嘅夢想飛翔，邁步向前<br />\n佢，只係一個氫氣球，我地都好清楚唔洗好耐佢就會跌翻落黎<br />\n今日天氣唔好，個氣球表面一多水珠就飛唔起<br />\n但佢都無懼風雨堅持起飛，希望為香港人帶黎一絲歡樂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以如果有人見到有個麵包超人飛過<br />\n麻煩留個言<br />\n如果可以搵翻留念當然好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算唔可以，可以博得全能嘅連登仔一笑<br />\n亦算係o係係世上發光發熱過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dF1uRbm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdF1uRbm.jpg&h=59c4347b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ffxNCRm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FffxNCRm.png&h=3695d800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qazhRn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qazhRn.png&h=75d5425e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一飛沖天去 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HBAoNIQMqNg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHBAoNIQMqNg&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8E6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=1d1db85e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HBAoNIQMqNg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後係向大埔方向飛去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最後可能去左樟樹灘村又或者唔識讀嘅<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>溋玥</strong></span>.天賦海灣</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">慢慢變成一點，係我視線中消失...</span>"},{"pid":"6dc6ce8030a4f7d6dccf3b16093c29398c2e5fc3","tid":1103831,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:20:53.000Z","msg":"。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"50e824fcf24f864853acda9e19c3f7d0e9a474b6","tid":1103831,"uid":188297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:23:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b26db2af554a694d6a2e39c096243746801afc70","tid":1103831,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710605796df492bd1feef3511394c3e3bc6a8931","tid":1103831,"uid":146215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:27:17.000Z","msg":"好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d8961e817aaab3c32b13701ab0ebc86376e1792","tid":1103831,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" cla